      "content": "a saline rinse sounds easy enough. is there like a specific way i should do it so i dont make it worse? and if i use like some drops or something i can get at the pharmacy should that do the trick instead of going to a doctor? i'm really hoping to just fix this at home so i don't have to deal with the clinic.",
